title: Tex-Mex Black Bean, Chorizo and Pepper Enchiladas with Plant-Based Cheese and Tortilla Chips
description: Enchiladas are pure comfort food – and a perfect way to eat more veggies! This dish features tortillas filled with DIY enchilada sauce, black beans, chorizo and sweet peppers, and they're topped with plant-based cheese and crispy crushed tortilla chips. Dinner is served!

